{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <h2>最新天文台天氣報告｜未來五天香港天氣預報</h2>\n    <p>天文台展望，明日及星期三部分時間有陽光，日間炎熱。隨後一兩日間中有驟雨，氣溫稍為下降。</p>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>4月20日(一)</cell>\n        <cell>4月21日(二)</cell>\n        <cell>4月22日(三)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>29度</cell>\n        <cell>29度</cell>\n        <cell>30度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>25度</cell>\n        <cell>25度</cell>\n        <cell>26度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>東至東南風2至3級。</cell>\n        <cell>南至東南風3至4級。</cell>\n        <cell>南風4級，間中5級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>70-95%</cell>\n        <cell>70-95%</cell>\n        <cell>70-95%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>中</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>中低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>部分時間有陽光。初時局部地區能見度頗低，稍後有幾陣驟雨及局部地區有雷暴。</cell>\n        <cell>部分時間有陽光，有一兩陣驟雨。日間炎熱。</cell>\n        <cell>部分時間有陽光。日間炎熱，稍後有幾陣驟雨。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>4月23日(四)</cell>\n        <cell>4月24日(五)</cell>\n        <cell>4月25日(六)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>27度</cell>\n        <cell>25度</cell>\n        <cell>26度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n        <cell>22度</cell>\n        <cell>22度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>南風4級，漸轉東北風4級。</cell>\n        <cell>東至東北風3至4級。</cell>\n        <cell>東至東北風4級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>80-95%</cell>\n        <cell>75-95%</cell>\n        <cell>75-95%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>中高</cell>\n        <cell>中</cell>\n        <cell>中低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，間中有驟雨及幾陣雷暴。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨，局部地區有雷暴。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。下午部分時間天色明朗。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-20T03:04:49.104771+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":494,"images":0,"source":"GoTrip","fallback":"none"}}